{"tid":2395590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"毒品調查科破獲4億港元販毒案 檢獲680公斤「K仔」","createTime":"2021-02-05T03:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T10:38:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1de04e565ed29c62701d79610188768368421f10","tid":2395590,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"警方毒品調查科破獲一宗4億港元販毒案，撿獲約680公斤俗稱「K仔」的氯胺酮，行動中拘捕1人。<br />\n<br />\n警方毒品調查科鄒旺忠警司交代案情稱，警方在元朗一個單位外截查1名23歲姓謝的無業漢，在他身上撿獲兩公斤K仔，隨後押入屋內搜查，再搜出5.5公斤K仔。警方隨後再押送疑犯到葵涌一個貨倉，再撿獲674.8公斤K仔。換言之合共682.3公斤氯胺酮，市值4億3,700萬元，是歷年以來就單一宗涉及K仔案件中最大份量。<br />\n<br />\n歹徒以通心粉及即食麵做包裝作掩飾，去年12月由巴基斯坦船運寄出，1月到港，毒品於1月底開始分銷港、九、新界各地。警方相信流出市面的毒品數量不多，大部份已經在今次行動中撿取。疑犯負責分銷，由貨倉提貨。他涉嫌販運危險藥物罪，明天（6日）在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210205/37F6CCFSVJF77JQ26XB7C6X4BM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210205%2F37F6CCFSVJF77JQ26XB7C6X4BM%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=5b94e661\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210205%2F37F6CCFSVJF77JQ26XB7C6X4BM%2F&h=6e857e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210205/37F6CCFSVJF77JQ26XB7C6X4BM/</a>"},{"pid":"9712125ba2428223d5a1a572caad73d44988cac6","tid":2395590,"uid":52779,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又搵𡃁仔出嚟頂<br />\n轉個頭咪又係運翻畀人"},{"pid":"596e34dde8abb807064d42b9eb4115d26d46e133","tid":2395590,"uid":96486,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"又可以入自己袋"},{"pid":"960dc6fce3a1553e2a6db1df387ffa805bda8caa","tid":2395590,"uid":44171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"如果係狗既家屬就馬上放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif